Quick explanation:

Chart.yaml â†’ Metadata about the chart.

values.yaml â†’ Default configuration that templates use.

templates/ â†’ Contains all your Kubernetes YAML templates.

.helmignore â†’ Ignore unnecessary files when packaging the chart.

